text: Concepción Ojeda Hernández (born 14 May 1977) is a Mexican politician from the Party of the Democratic Revolution. From 2006 to 2009 she served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Michoacán. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Michoacán Category:Women members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Party of the Democratic Revolution politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians Category:21st-century Mexican women politicians
title: Concepción Ojeda Hernández
